SUMMARY:Aspen to Birch Morning Forest Hike
DESCRIPTION:The Portland Hiking Meetup Group\n**Please note new 7:00AM start time!**\n\n**TOTAL DISTANCE:** 3.35 miles\n**ELEVATION GAIN:** \\~565 feet\n**PACE:** \\~ 2.5-3.0 mph depending on group speed.\n**ESTIMATED HIKING TIME:** \\~ 1hr 15 min\n**RATING:** Moderate+\n\nGet some wonderful time in the forest to get the day started! We start at the Aspen trailhead at 7:00\, hike up to join the Wildwood for a while\, then branch to the Birch Trail up to 53rd. We then take the reverse path back down\, with a goal to finish no later than 8:30.\n\n**Disclaimer:** Hike leaders are simply volunteers and try their best to make it a fun experience for everyone\, but assume no liability for any injury\, loss or damage. Every PHMG member is required to read our group's waiver\, and signing up or attending an event implies your approval.
